                            <msItem>
                                <locus from="1r" to="149v" scheme="folios"/>
                                <textLang mainLang="la"/>
                                <title type="desc">Report on the hearings of witnesses during Katarina's canonisation process, 1475-1477.</title>
                                <incipit defective="true">necnon meritis et miraculis dicte domine Katerine sancte memorie ac miraculorum eius crebrescencia et veritate admisimus </incipit>
                                <explicit>In quorum omnium et singulorum fidem et euidens Testimonium premissorum Sigilla nostra vnacum supscripcionibus notariorum seu scribarum nostrorum supra et infrascriptorum presentibus actis nostri apponi iussimus impendenda</explicit>
                                <colophon xml:lang="la">
                                    <locus from="149v" to="149v" scheme="folios"/>Datum in Ciuitate Strengenensi Anno domini Mcdlxx septimo die Martis Prima Mensis Iulii</colophon>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107255">Collijn (1942–1942)</title>
                                    <citedRange from="3" to="198" unit="page"/>
                                </bibl>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem>
                                <locus from="149v" to="152r" scheme="folios"/>
                                <textLang mainLang="la"/>
                                <title type="desc" xml:lang="la">Notarial acts</title>
                                <incipit>Et ego Conradus gregorii Clericus lincopensis diocesis publicus imperiali auctoritate notarius</incipit>
                                <explicit defective="false">Ideo hoc presens Registrum seu hec presencia acta manu alterius scripta et registrata de communi voluntate et requisicione prefatorum Dominorum Commissariorum subscripsi Signoque et nomine meis solitis et consuetis vnacum Dictorum Dominorum Commissariorum Sigillorum appensione signaui In fidem et testimonium omnium et singulorum premissorum Rogatus et requisitus</explicit>
                                <note>
                                    <locus from="152v" to="152v" scheme="folios"/> blank.</note>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107255">Collijn (1942–1942)</title>
                                    <citedRange from="198" to="200" unit="page"/>
                                </bibl>
                            </msItem>
                        </msContents>
